item.title: Stock market faces a midweek double whammy. Here's what to watch.
item.description: Circle Wednesday on your calendar. The stock market’s record-setting rally faces a midweek double whammy as a pivotal Federal Reserve’s interest-rate decision collides with a flood of megacap tech earnings — all unfolding against the backdrop of a prolonged government shutdown.
